title: Did you forget me ?
body: I have Riot Kayle but i did not recive anything, no icon, no mystery skin........ I hope u did not forget me xD

replies.body:
Depends if you were naughty or nice friend. 

You better keep playing,
you better not stop, 
better not rage, I'm telling you why, 
Riot is coming to take your {{champion:10}}

We did not forget you!  It's going to take time for everyone to get every gift, and they're being sent out individually.  You can stay updated at our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Just hang on until this is all done, and you'll get your goodies!
